<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>كِتَابُ الْجَنَائِزِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>قَدْ سَبَقَ فِي كِتَابِ الطَّهَارَةِ الْكَلَامُ فِي الْغُسْلِ مِنْ غُسْلِ الْمَيِّتِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">بَابُ:</span> الْإِعْلَامِ بِالْجَنَائِزِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>٢٢٩ - رَوَى حُذَيْفَةُ،<span class="c5"> عَنِ النَّبِيِّ صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«أَنَّهُ نَهَى عَنِ النَّعْيِ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>